contracts.name: TokenBridge
contracts.description: Contract used to bridge and escrow ERC-20 tokens.

contracts.name: CallForwardingProxy
contracts.description: A proxy contract forwarding calls to a predefined (immutable) target contract.

contracts.name: LineaRollup
contracts.description: The main contract of the Linea zkEVM rollup. Contains state roots, the verifier addresses and manages messages between L1 and the L2.

verifiers.description: Mapping of proof type to ZK Plonk Verifier contract

contracts.name: Timelock
contracts.description: A Timelock with currently 0s minimum delay.

contracts.name: Roles
contracts.description: The Zodiac roles module for Safe multisigs allows defining roles that are allowed to call preconfigured targets on behalf of the Gnosis Safe.
